				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Was told thru a necro friend about a 65 mage that claims his water pet can backstab for 32K hp? and can routinely tank against tier 2 mobs.
<br />

<br />
Now I am only level 40 but from what I have read on these boards I thought our pets were pretty weak at those levels and that is one of the on going discussions. I don't see how a 32K hp BS's pet is weak and I also don't see how one that can tank against tier 2 MOB's is weak.
<br />

<br />
Remember I am far from those levels but I have to take the claim with a bit of questioning. Can anyone give me some insight into this super pet?
<br />

<br />
I have the screen shot claiming it but I know that faking things in photoshop is trivial so................</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
