<span style="font-weight: bold">Now the facts. I never said it procced for 32k. I said it performed a rogue assasinate for 32k. It's extremely rare as I've seen it only twice and both times on mobs 46 and under so I'm sure there's a level cap on it as well. Once was a bouncer in Feerot (enclosed screenshot) and the other was when a chanter in Halls of Honor gated and her dire charmed pet turned on the group and the druid aggro kited it.
<br />
 
